					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hajovsky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7041744); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7041744&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610251593" alt="Dr Hajovsky" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7041744)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hajovsky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7041744); return false;" >Dr Hajovsky</a></span> <span class="odate time_1608943137 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">26 Dec 2020 00:38</span>
